overview: The Young Bucks (Matt Jackson & Nick Jackson) defeat ACH & Alex Shelley  Adam Cole defeats Moose (w/Stokely Hathaway)  reDRagon (Bobby Fish & Kyle O'Reilly) defeat The All-Night Express (Kenny King & Rhett Titus)  Dalton Castle (w/Brandon Tate & Brent Tate) defeats Delirious  Will Ferrara defeats Kevin Lee Davidson  The Briscoes (Jay Briscoe & Mark Briscoe) defeat Silas Young & The Beer City Bruiser  Roderick Strong (c) defeats Cheeseburger  Michael Elgin defeats Adam Page  War Machine (Hanson & Ray Rowe) defeat Chris Sabin & Frankie Kazarian
title: ROH: Winter Warriors Tour - Collinsville
